<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bienvenido(a)</title>
    <style>
        /* Variables de color */
        :root {
            --bg-light: #f4f4f4;
            --text-light: #333;
            --card-light: #ffffff;
            --shadow-light: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            --header-light: #173c2b;
            --footer-light: #4c4c4c;

            --bg-dark: #1a1a1a;
            --text-dark: #eaeaea;
            --card-dark: #222;
            --shadow-dark: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --header-dark: #444;
            --footer-dark: #333;
        }

        /* Estilos generales */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: var(--card-light);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--shadow-light);
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Modo oscuro */
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body {
                background-color: var(--bg-dark);
                color: var(--text-dark);
            }
            .container {
                background: var(--card-dark);
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--shadow-dark);
            }
            .header {
                background: var(--header-dark);
            }
            .footer {
                background: var(--footer-dark);
            }
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center; /* Centrar los logos */
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px; /* Espacio entre los logos */
            padding: 10px;
            background: var(--header-light);
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }


        .header img {
            max-height: 40px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        /* Botón de acción */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #fff;
            background: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }

        /* Pie de página */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background: var(--footer-light);
            border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://i0.wp.com/utd.edu.mx/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/LOGO-UTD-NUEVO-2022_solo-01.png?fit=1024%2C387&ssl=1" alt="Logo Izquierdo">
        <img src="https://images.freecreatives.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/logo007.png" alt="Logo Derecho">
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>Bienvenido(a), <strong>{{nombre}}</strong>!</h2>
        <p>Gracias por registrarte en nuestro sistema.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">Acceder a tu cuenta</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        © 2025 ErnestoOrtegaEnterprises.
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
